title: Numerous Updates to Correct URLs
body:
A large number of projects were still linking to CodePlex when active GitHub repositories or other repos existed. I've updated as well as noting where various projects are quite outdated, etc.

- Noted C# Native, OneDriveRestAPI, PocketSharp, TomP2P.NET, XamlEssentials, Zlip.Portable, SharpNLP, funq, Toxy, MicroSliver, Mugen Injection, StyleMVVM has no recent updates.
- Updated Essence#, IronScheme, Irony, Roslyn, SKGL, DNN, Mathos, MoreLINQ,  NodaTime, NPOI,  SharpMap, SharpSnmpLib, Web API Client Generator, WebSocket4Net, Nepy, Toxy, Magick.NET, .NET Image Processor, Simple Mvvm Toolkit, FsEye, Obfuscar, Protobuf-net, tickspec, fFastInjector, Unity Container URLs.
- Removed recommendation to look at CodePlex trending C# projects.
